OL,7,FA judicial spokesperson confirmed the
OL,8,Fjudges will hand down their ruling at
OL,9,F10am on Tuesday at the Royal Courts of
OL,10,FJustice in London, .
OL,12,FCalocane was sentenced for the fatal
OL,13,Fstabbings of students Mr Webber and Ms
OL,14,FO'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and 65-year-
OL,15,Fold school caretaker Mr Coates in the
OL,16,Fearly hours of June 13 last year.
OL,18,FAfter killing Mr Coates, Calocane
OL,19,Fstole his van and hit three
OL,20,Fpedestrians before being arrested.
