OL,3,CJudges to rule if Nottingham attacks
OL,4,Ctriple killer will have sentence
OL,5,Cchanged
OL,7,FLawyer Deanna Heer KC, representing
OL,8,Fthe Attorney General's Office, told
OL,9,Fthe court on Wednesday the "extreme"
OL,10,Fcrimes warrant "the imposition of a
OL,11,Fsentence with a penal element, an
OL,12,Felement of punishment".
OL,14,FPeter Joyce KC, representing Calocane,
OL,15,Fsaid none of the offences would have
OL,16,Fbeen committed "but for the
OL,17,Fpsychosis", and imposing a hybrid
OL,18,Forder would mean he would be "punished
OL,19,Ffor being mentally ill".
