OL,5,Cchanged
OL,7,FThe three judges determining whether
OL,8,FCalocane should have his sentence
OL,9,Fchanged are Baroness Carr, Lord
OL,10,FJustice Edis and Mr Justice Garnham.
OL,12,FHowever, they cannot examine or change
OL,13,Fthe offences for which Calocane was
OL,14,Fsentenced and cannot look at any new
OL,15,Fevidence related to the case.
OL,17,FInstead, they can only assess whether
OL,18,Fthe sentence was unduly lenient based
OL,19,Fon the evidence before the sentencing
OL,20,Fjudge at the time.
